<H2> A Taste of ESPRESSO </H2>
<H2> or <BR>
How to Use The San Pedro Martir <BR>
REOSC Echelle Spectrograph </H2>
<EM>S. Levine</EM> and
<EM>D. Chakrabarty</EM> <BR>
