<A NAME="tbuclpos"><EM>Table 5:</EM>
 Cross-Disperser angles for the UCL Camera</A>

<PRE>
Angle      Orders     Wavelength Range [&Aring;]
<P><HR><P>
352&#176;22&#180;    38-63      3497-5955 
353&#176;20&#180;    34-53      4157-6662 
353&#176;43&#180;    31-46      4790-7309          Gaps
355&#176;13&#180;    26-34      6487-8715          Gaps
356&#176;33&#180;    23-28      7869-9852          Gaps
<P><HR><P>
The wavelength range was empirically determined for 
CCD-Mil, and is about 20% greater for CCD-Tek. There 
are coverage gaps between some of the orders for those 
that say Gaps.
<P><HR><P>
</PRE>

