<P><HR><P>
a - dlambda/dx is the dispersion at the blaze wavelength.
b - FSR is the Free Spectral Range.
c - Delta lambda is an estimate of the wavelength span that 
    will fit on the chip, and is just the chip size times the
    dispersion at the blaze wavelength of the order.
<P><HR><P>
</PRE>

