<A NAME="tbmilgain"><EM>Table 9:</EM> CCD-Mil</A>
<PRE>

Gain     Well Depth at    Read Out Noise
Factor   A/D Saturation   (electrons)       e-/ADU
<P><HR><P>				  
1           173,000          5.71            10.6
2            86,500          4.48             5.3  
4            43,250          3.47             2.7
<P><HR><P>
All numbers (unless otherwise specified) are from 
the Photometrics documents supplied with the chips.
<P><HR><P>
</PRE>

<P><HR><A HREF="echelle.html">Return to Echelle Manual</A><HR><P>

