<HTML>
<TITLE>Figure 3: Inter-Order Spacing</TITLE>

<A HREF="echelle.html">Return to Echelle Manual</A>

<P><HR><P>
<A NAME="fgiosp">Figure 3: Inter-Order Spacing</A>
 <P>The inter-order spacing (at order center) on the image plane of
the two cameras (UCL camera on the left y-axis, REOSC camera on the
right y-axis).  The dashed lines show the length of the slit as it
is imaged upon the detector (<EM>w</EM> is the slit length of the
mask).  There is no overlap between adjacent orders with spacing above
the line that corresponds to the slit length.


<IMG SRC="fig_iosp.gif" WIDTH=805 HEIGHT=750 >

