<A NAME="t6"><EM>TABLA 6.</EM> VENTANA DE COMANDOS DEL PROGRAMA CAMILA</A>

<PRE>
           C A M I L A (v.7/93)
<STRONG>obj</STRONG> ... nada

<STRONG>ar</STRONG>       0.0       <STRONG>dec</STRONG>       0.      <STRONG>ma</STRONG>  1.00
<STRONG>ofs</STRONG>      0.0       0.0


<STRONG>fil</STRONG>      0       <STRONG>arch</STRONG>  kk001
<STRONG>sec</STRONG>   una (de   1 pasos)
  tmu     0.0   tlec    0.0
<STRONG>nlec</STRONG>    2     <STRONG>nadd</STRONG>    1       <STRONG>sat</STRONG> 17000


<STRONG>c1 c2 c3 </STRONG>  1.05   0.10E-04   0.00E+00
<STRONG>io1 io2 io3 io4</STRONG>  600  600  600  600


<STRONG>tint</STRONG>    0.5   ttot     0.5   tcuadro 0.46

status: ESPERANDOTE

<STRONG>&gt;</STRONG>

</PRE>

<P><HR>
<A HREF="camila.html">Return to Camila Manual</A>
