<TITLE>Seminar Schedule - Fall 1995</TITLE>

<CENTER>
<H2>
IA-UNAM-Ensenada 1995<BR>
Fall Seminar Schedule:
</H2>
<IMG SRC="/Gifs/redball.gif"> marks upcoming seminar(s).
</CENTER>

<P> For those of you interested in recent history, take a peak at 
the <A HREF="./Sem_Spr95.html">Spring Semester, 1995</A> schedule.

<IMG SRC="/Gifs/hrainbow.gif" ALIGN=center 
ALT="------------------------------------------------------------">
<P>
    
<DL>

<DT> Wed. 20 Sept -- <EM>Mauricio Tapia</EM> (IA-UNAM, Ensenada)
<DD> "Highlights and Lowlights from the Meeting on the Role of Dust in
      Star Formation Regions"

<DT> Wed 27 Sep --<EM>Stephen Levine</EM> (IA-UNAM,Ensenada)
<DD> "Smashing Results from the Meeting on Interacting Galaxies"
 
<DT> Tue 3 Oct -- <EM>Kate Scholberg</EM> (Caltech, Pasadena)
<DD> "Searching for Neutrinos from Gravitational Collapse with the
     MACRO Experiment" 
 
<DT> Wed 11 Oct -- <EM>Fidel Cruz</EM> (IA-UNAM,Ensenada)
<DD> "Construcci&oacute;n de un Cumulo Globular"

<DT> 16-20 Oct -- ZEUS Group, Taller II

<DT> Wed 25 Oct -- <EM>Mauricio Reyes</EM> (IA-UNAM, Ensenada)
<DD> "Sistemas Proto-Planetaria"

<DT> 28-29 Nov -- Taller sobre ``ESTADO ACTUAL Y PERSPECTIVAS DEL OAN''
 
<DT> <A NAME="current"><IMG SRC="/Gifs/redball.gif"></A>
     Fri 8 Dec -- <EM>Alex Raga</EM> (IA-UNAM, DF)
<DD> "Collisions of Jets with Dense Objects"

</DL>

<P>All seminars are at 12:00 noon in the auditorium, unless otherwise
specified, and feature coffee and cookies.<P>

