Alamos Science</i></a> - <i>PDF format</i> necesitar&aacute;n tener el Acrobat
Reader de Adobe - gratis en el sitio de <i><a href= "http://lib-www.lanl.gov/la-pubs/la-pubs.htm">Los Alamos Publications</i></a>.

	</ul>


<p>

<li> Recursos para la ense&ntilde;anza de la F&iacute;sica:
	<ul>
	<li> Noticias en F&iacute;sica <a href= "http://www.het.brown.edu/news/"><i>Physics News</i></a> e informaci&oacute;n <i><a href= "http://info.desy.de/user/projects/Physics.html">Phys_Info</i></a>.
	<li><a href=
"http://www-hpcc.astro.washington.edu/scied/physics.html"><i>PhysicsED </i></a>.
	<li>El Contemporary Physics Education Project <i><a href= "http://www-pdg.lbl.gov/cpep.html">CPEP</i></a>.
	<li>Cursos de F&iacute;sica en el Massachusetts Institute
of Technology <i><a href= "http://web.mit.edu/physics/www/physics.html">(MIT) Physics Department</i></a>:
		<ul>
		<li><i><a href= "http://web.mit.edu/8.01/www/">Physics I</i></a>.
		<li><i><a href= "http://web.mit.edu/afs/athena/course/8/8.04/804f.html"> Quantum Physics I</i></a>
		<li><i><a href= "http://web.mit.edu/afs/athena/course/8/8.13/3LHomePage.html">
Experimental Physics</i></a>.
		</ul>
	<li><i><a href= "http://bohr.physics.purdue.edu/~phys220/homepage.html">Introductory
Mechanics at Purdue</i></a>
	<li> Textos y cursos de F&iacute;sica:
		<ul>
		<li>Libro Virtual de F&iacute;sica <a href="http://uptown.turnpike.net/L/lindeman/physics_ub.html"><i>
Physics Unbound </a></i>. 
		<li><a href= "http://www-hpcc.astro.washington.edu/scied/physics/physcourse.html">
<i>Physics Courses and Hypertext Topics</i></a>.
