40. S. Kent. <A NAME=id HREF="http://www.cis.ohio-state.edu:82/rfc/rfc1422.html">RFC 1422</A>: Privacy Enhancement for Internet Electronic Mail, 
    Part II: Certificate-Based Key Management. Internet Activities Board, 
    February 1993.

