<CENTER><A HREF="#EDTITOR"><H4>Letter to the Editor</H4></A></CENTER>

<CENTER><A HREF="#FEEDBACK"><H4>Feedback about the web site</H4></A></CENTER><BR>

<BR>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="SUCCESS">About Success</A></H3>
<p><FONT SIZE=+1>SUCCESS is the only magazine for today's entrepreneurial mind. It is written for business owners, entrepreneurs, and entrepreneurial thinkers, with all the editorial aimed at improving their personal and organizational effectiveness. The building blocks of the magazine's editorial are the principles, concepts, techniques and methods of entrepreneurial management, with a heavy emphasis on technology. SUCCESS covers all phases of the entrepreneurial life cycle, including venture creation, marketing, selling and automation, as well as the entrepreneurial lifestyle and strategies for cashing out. It is all practical, personally relevant editorial aimed at helping the reader expand a business in today's competitive marketplace.</FONT></P>


<HR>
<H3><A NAME="SUBCRIBE">Subscribe</A></H3>
<FONT SIZE=+1><A HREF="./subinfo.html">Click here</A> for information on subscriptions to Success</FONT>

 <HR>
 
<H3><A NAME="BACK">Back Issues</A></H3>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>To order back issues within the U.S. and Canada call (800) 967-2083. 

To order back issues outside the U.S. and Canada call (515) 246-6911. 

The fax number is (515) 246-6933. 

Back issues are $5.00 for the first copy and $4.00 thereafter, if ordering less than ten copies. For orders of ten or more copies, the cost is $2.00 per issue.</FONT></P>

<HR>

<H3><A NAME="REPRINTS">Reprints</A></H3>

<FONT SIZE=+1>To obtain 100 or more reprints of an article call (201) 575- 1073 

To obtain permission to copy an article in quantities of less than 100, contact Lucille Gannon at (212) 551-9422. </FONT>

<HR>

<H3><A NAME="SERVICE">Customer Service</A></H3>

<FONT SIZE=+1>For customer service in the U.S. or Canada call (800) 234-7324.<BR> 

For customer service outside the U.S. or Canada call (515) 247-7569.</FONT><BR> 

