<p><DIV ALIGN="CENTER"><FONT SIZE=+1>Success is published monthly except for January and July.</FONT></P>
<BR>
<BR>
<HR>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>Subscription for one year (10 issues) is $19.97; two years $29.97.  Canada add $8 a year for postage and GST.  All other foreign countries add $11. Cover price is $3.00. Please allow 6-8 weeks for delivery of first issue. </FONT></P>

<HR>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1>For bulk subscription rates (10 or more copies),<BR> 
call Mary Crawford (212) 883-7133.</FONT></P>

