	<FONT SIZE="+4">An Electronic Guide <BR>For the <BR>Entrepreneur</FONT>
<H3>How to Find <BR>Competitive Intelligence -- <BR>Everywhere </H3>

</TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN=RIGHT VALIGN=TOP COLSPAN="1" ROWSPAN="1"><FONT SIZE="-1">Illustration By Peter Hoey</FONT></TD/<Td></Td>





