<DOCHDR>
http://www.successmagazine.com:80/archives.html/jan97.html/1EdNote.html 199.92.136.187 19970114134330 text/html 6040
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 13:40:46 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 10-Jan-97 15:34:54 GMT
