<DOCHDR>
http://www.successmagazine.com:80/archives.html/jan97.html/1harrell.html 199.92.136.187 19970114134828 text/html 6307
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 13:45:40 GMT
