	<TD></TD>

	<TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=MIDDLE COLSPAN="1" ROWSPAN="1">
	<IMG SRC="logo%203.jpeg" ALIGN=ABSMIDDLE WIDTH="144" HEIGHT="64"><BR>

<H4 ALIGN=LEFT><FONT COLOR="#CC000C">November 1996<BR><BR></FONT> </H4>
	</TD>

</TR>
<TR ALIGN=left VALIGN=TOP>

	<TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP COLSPAN="1" ROWSPAN="1">
	
<P><H3>FEATURES</H3></P>


<H5>COVER STORY:</H5> <FONT SIZE="+1"><A HREF="./cover%20story.html">THE MONEY-HUNTER MINDSET</A>  There are two sides to every story -- the entrepreneur's and the investor's. You need to know both to land the best deal. </FONT>
<BR><HR><BR>

