	<TD ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=TOP COLSPAN="2" ROWSPAN="1">
	<FONT SIZE="+5">The Money-Hunter Mindset</FONT><BR><FONT SIZE="+1">How Thinking Like an Investor Will Put You on the Road to Riches</FONT>
	</TD>
