http://www.successmagazine.com:80/archives.html/oct96.%20html/10Franchising1.html 199.92.136.187 19970114142828 text/html 13634
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 14:25:38 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 10-Oct-96 18:03:32 GMT
Content-length: 13442
