Ill. 60045. Private consulting to family-owned businesses; 847-295-1040.
</P>

<P>The Family Firm Institute, 12 Harris St., Brookline, Mass. 02146. 617-738-1591.
Professional association of family business consultants; publishes Family
Business Review magazine. Web site: <A HREF="http://ffi.org">http://ffi.org</A>. </P>

