<P ALIGN=CENTER><FONT COLOR="#FF0000">FRANCHISING: SUCCESS SELECTS </FONT></P>

<P ALIGN=CENTER><FONT SIZE=+3>Retail Superstars </FONT></P>

<P>More than any other sector, retail leads the growth of franchising. The
principles by which sound retail businesses are established and developed
are the fundamentals for creating a franchise model: systems, training,
buying, and product strategies. No sector creates stronger, more reliable
franchise models than retail, and the following companies -- selected from
the 1995 SUCCESS Gold 100 listing -- are among the best. </P>

