<CENTER><P> </P></CENTER><BR><BR>

 <CENTER><FONT SIZE="+4">Food, Glorious Food</FONT>
</CENTER>

<P>
Many of the hottest franchise concepts are food-related businesses. This market includes everything from fast food and full-service restaurants to niche foods such as bagels and gourmet coffee. 

