<FONT COLOR="#F80003">SPECIAL BOOK BONUS </FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="+7">The ThighMaster <BR>Exercise Bonanza</FONT>

<H2>How to Create A $100 Million Craze </H2>

<FONT SIZE="+1"><B>By Peter Bieler With Suzanne Costas</B></FONT> 
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE="+1">John Lennon quipped that the Beatles were more famous than Jesus. I
won't make that mistake. I will say, however, that if you haven't heard
of ThighMaster exerciser, you've been shipwrecked on a deserted island
or you're still in Pampers; either way, you won't be reading this book.
 Me? I'm the guy behind the ThighMaster success, a dubious distinction
unless you appreciate the difficulties inherent in capturing the attention
of the whole country -- in selling six million ThighMasters in less than
two years -- without a war chest the size of General Motors. In fact, the
phenomenon that grossed more than $100 million started in a modest office
with three people.  How did I do it? </FONT>
<HR><BR>
<DIV ALIGN=CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="0" CELLPADDING="1" CELLSPACING="5" WIDTH="470">

