<DOCHDR>
http://www.successmagazine.com:80/archives.html/oct96.%20html/10king.html 199.92.136.187 19970114142449 text/html 9336
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 14:21:58 GMT
